## âœ… Your Frontend Will Call This

Your DevOps extension can now send a POST to this Azure Function instead of directly triggering the pipeline. This way:

* âœ… PAT is never exposed to the browser
* âœ… Complies with Azure DevOps CSP
* âœ… Easier to audit and secure

